entities.name: Auto.fun

entities.name: Comput3

entities.name: DOOD

entities.name: Shaw
entities.description: An individual who commented on AI agents, suggesting a focus on fundamental GPT-class problems rather than shallow agent builders.

entities.name: Github

entities.name: Ollama

entities.name: Bun
entities.description: A fast JavaScript runtime, bundler, and package manager. Logo is a white bun/dumpling on black.

entities.name: Node.js

entities.name: Doodles

entities.name: Kenk

entities.name: Virtuals
